text: Alix Didier Fils-Aimé is a Haitian businessman and politician who has been the acting Prime Minister of Haiti since 10 November 2024. He was the president of the Chamber of Commerce of Haiti in the government of the former president Michel Martelly. ==References== Category:Prime ministers of Haiti Category:Living people Category:1971 births Category:Current national leaders Category:Business people Category:Economists
